          "content": {
            "size": 7928,
            "mimeType": "text/html",
            "text": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"utf-8\"/>\n  <!-- Meta -->\n  <link href=\"/favicon.ico?1684136885\" type=\"image/x-icon\" rel=\"icon\"/><link href=\"/favicon.ico?1684136885\" type=\"image/x-icon\" rel=\"shortcut icon\"/>  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, shrink-to-fit=yes\"/>  <meta name=\"google\" content=\"notranslate\"/>  \n  <!-- Title -->\n  <title>\n    壽司郎 歡迎光臨: Home  </title>\n\n  <!-- Styles -->\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/css/user/user.css?1684136885\"/>  </head>\n\n<body>\n  <header class=\"header\">\n    <div class=\"header__wrapper\">\n        <h1>\n            <img src=\"/img/logo/Sushiro_logo_user.png?1684136885\" alt=\"sushiro logo\" class=\"header__logo\" decoding=\"async\"/>        </h1>\n    </div>\n</header>\n  <main id=\"app\">\n        <section class=\"section\" v-if=\"surveyForms\" v-cloak>\n  <div class=\"survey survey--no-padding\" id=\"questionsPage\">\n    <h2 class=\"survey__title survey__title--with-padding\" v-show=\"questionTitle !== null\">{{ questionTitle }}</h2>\n    <div class=\"survey__content-wrapper\">\n      <form class=\"form question\">\n        <ul class=\"question__list\">\n          <li class=\"question__item\" v-for=\"question in questions\">\n            <label class=\"form__label\" v-html=\"question.content\"></label>\n              <component \n                :is=\"getOptionType(question.form_type)\" \n                :list=\"question.options\" \n                :type=\"getOptionType(question.form_type)\" \n                :name=\"question.id\" \n                v-if=\"getOptionType(question.form_type) == 'radio' || getOptionType(question.form_type) == 'checkbox'\"\n                :required=\"question.is_required\"\n                ></component>\n              <component :is=\"getOptionType(question.form_type)\" :name=\"question.id\" v-else></component>\n              <p class=\"form__error\" v-if=\"errorMessage.includes(question.id)\">必須項目</p>\n          </li>\n        </ul>\n      </form>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"survey__action-wrapper\">\n      <button class=\"button\"\n      @click.prevent=\"validateForm\">下一頁</button>\n      <div class=\"progress\">\n        <div class=\"progress__wrapper\">\n          <p class=\"progress__text\">{{progress}}% 完成</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n    <section class=\"section\" v-if=\"startForm\" v-cloak>\n  <div class=\"survey\">\n    <h2 class=\"survey__title\">感謝您蒞臨壽司郎用餐</h2>\n    <p class=\"survey__paragraph\">為了提升本店服務品質，將進行以下問卷調查</p>\n    <p class=\"survey__paragraph\">麻煩您撥冗協助填寫。</p>\n          <p class=\"survey__paragraph\">本問卷所得資料僅作為本公司提升服務品質之使用，決不做任何對外用途，敬請放心填寫並會依壽司郎個人資料保護方針進行管理。</p>\n            <p class=\"survey__paragraph\">本問卷調查建議使用智慧型手機、平板電腦、筆記型電腦、桌上型電腦進行填寫。</p>\n    <div class=\"survey__link-wrapper\">\n          <a class=\"survey__link\" href=\n        http://www.akindo-sushiro.co.jp/apps/cn/privacy/      target=\"_blank\">請閱讀「台灣壽司郎股份有限公司個人資料保護原則」</a>\n        </div>\n    <form class=\"form\" @submit.prevent=\"startingSurvey\">\n            <div class=\"form__group\">\n        <label>\n          <input type=\"checkbox\" v-model=\"buttonState\">\n          <span class=\"form__option-text\">我已仔細閱讀並同意「台灣壽司郎股份有限公司個人資料保護原則」</span>\n        </label>\n      </div>\n            <div class=\"form__group\">\n        <label class=\"form__label\">請輸入折價券聯上的邀請序號。</label>\n        <input class=\"form__input\" type=\"number\" name=\"invitation_code\" v-model=\"invitationCode\">\n        <p class=\"form__error\" v-if=\"errorInvitationCode !=''\">{{errorInvitationCode}}</p>\n      </div>\n              <div class=\"form__group\">\n          <label class=\"form__label\">請輸入發票上的消費金額。</label>\n          <input class=\"form__input form__input--small\" type=\"number\" v-model=\"price\" :step=\"false\">\n          <p class=\"form__error\" v-if=\"errorPrice !=''\">{{errorPrice}}</p>\n        </div>\n            <div class=\"form__group\">\n        <label class=\"form__label\">請選擇您用餐的時間</label>\n        <div class=\"form__radio-group\">\n          <label>\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"visited_time\" value=\"1\" v-model=\"visitTime\">\n            <span class=\"form__option-text\">～14時</span>\n          </label>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"form__radio-group\">\n          <label>\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"visited_time\" value=\"2\" v-model=\"visitTime\">\n            <span class=\"form__option-text\">14時～17時</span>\n          </label>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"form__radio-group\">\n          <label>\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"visited_time\" value=\"3\" v-model=\"visitTime\">\n            <span class=\"form__option-text\">17時～21時</span>\n          </label>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"form__radio-group\">\n          <label>\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"visited_time\" value=\"4\" v-model=\"visitTime\">\n            <span class=\"form__option-text\">21時～</span>\n          </label>\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"form__error\" v-if=\"errorVisitTime !=''\">{{errorVisitTime}}</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"survey__button-wrapper\">\n              <button class=\"button\" :disabled=\"!buttonState\">開始</button>\n            </div>\n    </form>\n  </div>\n</section>    <section class=\"section\" v-if=\"startSurvey\" v-cloak>\n  <div class=\"survey\">\n    <div class=\"survey__content-wrapper\">\n      <h2 class=\"survey__title\">本問卷填寫完畢後，會顯示一組5位數的認證碼。將認證碼紀錄在折價券聯上的對應欄位(小方框内)，下次來店消費時即可做為折價券使用，請妥善保存。</h2>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"survey__action-wrapper\">\n      <div class=\"survey__button-wrapper\">\n        <button class=\"button\" @click=\"loadFirstQuestion\">開始</button>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>    <section class=\"section\" v-if=\"surveyComplete\" v-cloak>\n  <div class=\"survey\">\n    <div class=\"survey__container\">\n      <h2 class=\"survey__title survey__title--complete\">請確認折價券內容。</h2>\n      <p class=\"survey__paragraph\">請將以下認證碼填入折價券的對應欄位</p>\n      <p class=\"survey__paragraph survey__paragraph--promo-code\">{{promoCode}}</p>\n      <p class=\"survey__paragraph\">消費結帳時，請將折價券與結帳號碼牌一起交給結帳人員，即可獲得對應的折價優惠。</p>\n      <p class=\"survey__paragraph\">非常感謝您的合作，並誠摰期待您再度蒞臨台灣壽司郎門市。</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"survey__link-container\">\n        <label class=\"survey__title survey__title--complete\">\n          前往台灣壽司郎官網        </label>\n\n                \n        <div class=\"survey__link-wrapper survey__link-wrapper--home\">\n          <a class=\"survey__link\" href=https://sushiro.com.tw/ target=\"_blank\">\n            請點選此連結          </a>\n        </div>\n\n              </div>\n      </div>\n</section>  </main>\n\n  <footer class=\"footer\">\n    <div class=\"footer__wrapper\">\n                    <a href=\n                http://www.akindo-sushiro.co.jp/apps/cn/privacy/            class=\"footer__link\" target=\"_blank\">\n                akindosushiro個人資料保護方針            </a>\n            </div>\n</footer>  <div class=\"loading\">\n  <div class=\"loading__overlay\">\n    <img src=\"/img/icon/loading-icon.gif\" alt=\"loading gif\" class=\"loading__gif\">\n  </div>\n</div>\n  <script>\n    const APIKEY = \"web:624a677331626b5044e9bb25a1fcf8a9\";\n  </script>\n\n  <!-- Scripts -->\n  \n\t<script src=\"/js/vendor/axios/axios.min.js?1684136885\"></script>\n\t<script src=\"/js/vendor/vue/vue.min.js?1684136885\"></script>\n\n  <script src=\"/js/user/user.js?1684136885\"></script></body>\n\n</html>"
          },
